<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kelly Kay Massage</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Kelly Kay Massage</h1>
    <p>Relax • Refresh • Restore</p>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
        <h2>Experience Deep Relaxation & Professional Massage Therapy</h2>
        <p>
            Escape from stress and enjoy a relaxing massage session designed
            to help your body feel renewed and refreshed.
        </p>

        <a href="#booking" class="button">Book Your Session</a>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="about">
    <h2>About Kelly Kay Massage</h2>
    <p>
        At Kelly Kay Massage, we provide professional massage experiences
        in a calm and comfortable environment. Our goal is to help you
        relax, release tension, and feel your best.
    </p>
</section>


<section class="services">
    <h2>Our Services</h2>

    <div class="service-box">
        <h3>Swedish Massage</h3>
        <p>Gentle relaxation massage to reduce stress and improve wellbeing.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-box">
        <h3>Deep Tissue Massage</h3>
        <p>Focused massage to release muscle tension and body stress.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-box">
        <h3>Relaxation Session</h3>
        <p>A peaceful experience to help you recharge and feel refreshed.</p>
    </div>

</section>


<section id="booking" class="booking">
    <h2>Ready To Relax?</h2>
    <p>Reserve your massage appointment today.</p>

    <a href="#" class="button">Make A Reservation</a>
</section>


<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Kelly Kay Massage. All Rights Reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
